text: Groß-Gerau is a Kreis (district) in the south of Hesse, Germany. The river Main forms the northern boundary of the district, the river Rhine the western border. ==Towns and municipalities== Towns Municipalities #Gernsheim #Ginsheim-Gustavsburg #Groß-Gerau #Kelsterbach #Mörfelden-Walldorf #Raunheim #Riedstadt #Rüsselsheim #Biebesheim #Bischofsheim #Büttelborn #Nauheim #Stockstadt am Rhein #Trebur ==References==
